<p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 249, 244); font-size: 24px;">蔡紫欣、钟宝乐、陈淑娟、陈美瑜、祝诏谆5名同志将自己在考察阶段的表现分别从思想、工作等方面的培养情况向党组织进行了详细汇报，并充分表达了自己坚定的入党决心。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 249, 244); font-size: 24px;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEIZHPicqGZs6LL0QqEnwXYAvOYI4npoiabDuSpbA2VzcT0fWqsSlRpJN0QxTkZruGtkwTWTicb99BrMg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&wxfrom=13&tp=wxpic" alt="图片" width="324" height="192" style="width: 324px; height: 192px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 249, 244); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.57em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">五位同志的培养联系人对其有关情况进行说明并对其能否被发展为预备党员表明意见。与会党员充分交换意见，进行充分讨论后，通过无记名填写表决票的方式进行表决。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 249, 244); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.57em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">大会认为：蔡紫欣、钟宝乐、陈淑娟、陈美瑜、祝诏谆五名同志已基本具备党员条件，同意吸收为中共预备党员。</span></p><p><br/></p>